| Benefit                   | Description                                             |
| ------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------- |
| **No downtime**           | System stays online even if one server fails            |
| **Better performance**    | Can handle sudden spikes in users                       |
| **Cost efficiency**       | Pay only for the resources you use                      |
| **Customer satisfaction** | Fast, reliable, always-available apps                   |
| **Business continuity**   | No interruptions â€” your business keeps running smoothly |

